Package com.chairbender.object_calisthenics_analyzer.violation

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FirstClassCollectionsViolation
    Represents a violation of having a class that has a collections member and some other members Created by chairbender on 11/21/2015.
    KeepEntitiesSmallViolation
    Represents a violation of having more than 50 lines in a class Created by chairbender on 11/21/2015.
    NoElseStatementViolation
    Represents a violation of using an else statement.
    NoGettersSettersViolation
    Represents a violation of having an obvious getter or setter Created by chairbender on 11/21/2015.
    OneDotPerLineViolation
    Represents a violation of using more than one "dot" in a line Created by chairbender on 11/21/2015.
    SingleLevelOfIndentationViolation
    Represents a violation of having more than one level of indentation inside a method.
    TwoOrFewerFieldsViolation
    Represents a violation of having more than two fields in a class Created by chairbender on 11/21/2015.
    Violation
    Represents a violation of one of the object calisthenics rules Created by chairbender on 11/21/2015.
    ViolationMonitor
    Listens for and stores all of the violation of a given collection of source code.
    WrapAllPrimitivesAndStringsViolation
    Represents a violation of not wrapping a primitive or a string.
